.TH TALLY 1 "May 2015"
.SH NAME
tally \- count lines of source code
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tally
[\fIOPTION\fR] [\fIPATH\fR]...
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-s
show line counts per language (default)
.TP
.B \-i
show line counts per file
.TP
.B \-d
show detected file types
.TP
.B \-h
show usage information
